videos.description: David Blough's play-action flip ends up in the hands of D.J. Knox, who dives towards the pylon and sneaks into the end zone on an 18-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Knox hits pylon for score

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor busts loose for an 80-yard touchdown on Wisconsin's first play of the second half.
videos.headline: Taylor breaks free for long TD to open 2nd half

videos.description: Purdue RB Markell Jones sheds a tackle and makes a swift cut on a Wisconsin defender as he swerves in for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones slices into end zone for TD

videos.description: David Blough lofts a pass over the middle to Rondale Moore, who shakes a defender and chugs to the end zone for a 46-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Moore shakes defender on 46-yard TD

videos.description: Wisconsin WR Danny Davis III snags a Jack Coan back-shoulder fade with one hand to complete an insane 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Davis goes full OBJ on spectacular 1-handed TD

videos.description: Jack Coan whips a pretty pass to Danny Davis III, who leaps and makes a beautiful 18-yard touchdown catch to knot the score at 27-27.
videos.headline: Davis snatches second TD of 4th Qtr

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Jonathan Taylor motors his way into the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown to force a second overtime vs. Purdue.
videos.headline: Wisconsin retaliates in OT with 12-yard Taylor TD

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Garrett Groshek takes the handoff and dives towards the goal line for a 4-yard touchdown in the second overtime.
videos.headline: Groshek breaks plane for TD in second OT

videos.description: David Blough drops a dime to Isaac Zico for a 25-yard score on Purdue's first play of its second overtime possession.
videos.headline: Zico hauls in beautiful TD in second OT

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor's third touchdown comes in the third overtime, giving Wisconsin a thrilling 47-44 victory vs. Purdue.
videos.headline: Taylor caps off 300-plus yard day with game-winning TD
